        "TileImage": "$($repository 4d4ee135-ef81-4b66-8149-ad774fb34970).Image",
        "Description": "47, The Vertex is infiltrating global agencies to seize the U.S. Gold Reserves.\r\rTargets:\r\rJimmy (Technician): A substance-addicted asset who created a digital backdoor for Vertex. Eliminate him to seal the breach.\r\rAny (Enforcer): A serial killer posing as a job seeker. She’s finished her interview and is awaiting the signal to kill the board. She frequently updates her husband, a Vertex runner.\rThe bank remains vital to the U.S. government. Avoid collateral damag\rStop the takeover. Good luck.",
